name: Saboor Ahmed

services.title: Custom Software Development
services.description: We provide custom software development services tailored to your business needs using technologies like PHP (Laravel), Python (Django, Flask), Node.js, and React. Our solutions ensure scalability, security, and seamless integration for web and mobile applications.

services.title: Web Development
services.description: Our web development services include both frontend and backend development, creating fast, responsive, and scalable web applications. We specialize in Next.js, React, Vue.js, and Angular for the frontend, and Node.js, PHP (Laravel), and Python (Django, Flask) for the backend, ensuring high performance and security.

services.title: Web Design
services.description: Our web design services focus on creating visually stunning, user-friendly, and responsive designs that enhance user experience. We use Figma, Adobe XD, and Sketch to craft modern UI/UX designs, ensuring seamless navigation and brand consistency across all devices.

services.title: 3D Design
services.description: Our 3D design services bring ideas to life with high-quality modeling, rendering, and animations. We use Blender, 3ds Max, and Cinema 4D to create realistic visuals for branding, product design, architecture, and immersive experiences.

services.title: BlockChain Development
services.description: Our blockchain development services include smart contract development, decentralized applications (dApps), NFT marketplaces, and cryptocurrency wallets using Ethereum, Solana, Binance Smart Chain, and Hyperledger. We ensure secure, scalable, and transparent blockchain solutions for various industries.

services.title: Mobile App Development
services.description: Our mobile app development services cover Android and iOS applications using React Native, Flutter, Swift, and Kotlin. We build high-performance, user-friendly, and scalable mobile apps tailored to your business needs, ensuring a seamless user experience.

aboutpara: I lead a dedicated team of 10 skilled developers and designers, delivering high-quality digital solutions. With 4 years of experience as a developer and business development executive lead, I specialize in web and mobile app development, UI/UX design, and blockchain solutions. My expertise in both technical development and strategic business growth ensures that our team creates innovative, scalable, and results-driven solutions for clients worldwide.

resume.description: With 4 years of experience as a developer and business development executive lead, I specialize in web and mobile app development, UI/UX design, and blockchain solutions. My expertise in both technical development and strategic business growth enables me to deliver innovative, scalable, and results-driven solutions for clients worldwide
